it.uniroma1.lcl.babelnet

Class BabelPointer

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.uniroma1.lcl.babelnet.BabelPointer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.mit.jwi.item.IPointer, java.io.Serializable

    public class BabelPointer
extends java.lang.Object
implements edu.mit.jwi.item.IPointer, java.io.Serializable
    Default, hard-coded, implementation of IPointer for BabelNet. Models a semantic pointer in BabelNet. Includes an associative (ie semantically unspecified) relation.
    See Also:
    IPointer, Serialized Form
